OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIncreasingly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with the chance of
OL,7,Fa few spots of light rain. Later in
OL,8,Fthe night, clearer spells develop for
OL,9,Fa time, before further rain spreading
OL,10,Fsoutheast, heavy at times and
OL,11,Faccompanied by freshening winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRather cloudy during the
OL,14,Fmorning, with rain spreading
OL,15,Fsoutheast, occasionally heavy at
OL,16,Ffirst. Then turning drier and brighter
OL,17,Finto the afternoon with just a few
OL,18,Flight showers. Fresh winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
