OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain clearing
OL,7,FSunday morning, bright spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers in afternoon. Fairly
OL,9,Funsettled and changeable Monday and
OL,10,FTuesday with the risk of rain or
OL,11,Fshowers.
